Noun affixes:

* diminuative --> + otz
* superlative --> + uk
* derogatory --> + ax
* beautificatory --> + im --> ilm
* all --> + ek
* not --> + um
* interrogative --> + it
* indefinite (some) --> + ap
* masc / neut / fem --> + u + o + a
* definite (the) --> + (j)e

